high_descs: Move to the island left of the tomato.
Pick up the potato that is left of the tomato.
Move to the island left of the tomato.
Put the potato on the island.
Pick up the knife that is on the island nearest the tomato.
Slice the potato on the island.
Put the knife on the island.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the microwave.
Put the potato slice into the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move the the trash bin that is right of the refrigerator.
Put the cooked potato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a microwaved slice of potato.

high_descs: Walk to the opposite side of the kitchen island
Grab the potato off of the counter
Look at the entire counter
Put the potato on the counter
Grab the large knife off of the counter
Cut the potato into slices
Put the knife down on the counter
Grab one of the slices of potato
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the potato in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and locate the trash can
Put the potato in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Throwing a potato slice in the trash can

high_descs: Go around the island to the other side.
Pick up the potato on the counter top.
Examine the potato.
Place the potato back on the counter top.
Pick up the long knife behind the potato.
Slice the potato on the counter top.
Split the sliced potato from the rest.
Take one slice of the potato.
Turn left to go to the microwave.
Microwave the potato slice next to the apple and take it out.
Turn around to go to the trash can at the end of the counter.
Place the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a heated slice of potato.
